data.description:
This stand alone home has a lovely floor plan with a bedroom on each side of the spacious Great Room, Dining Room and Kitchen There are only two stairs in the whole house and there is an oversized, attached, two car garage. The floors throughout are Saltillo tile. The Living Room has a tongue-in-groove wood ceiling with beams between the rooms and a corner fireplace for cozy winter evenings. The dining room has a French door leading to a large wrap-around and freshly painted deck, fenced for privacy and lined with abundant grapevines. The kitchen has a bar that separates it from the dining room but is open and could be perfect for entertaining. Sellers recently had the whole house painted.

Park Plazas is a unique oasis, centrally located in Santa Fe. With miles of walking trails, an off-leash dog park, tennis and pickleball courts and a community garden this neighborhood is the perfect mix of city and country living. Don’t miss this home!
